modules.description: This module provides functions to build and run interactive command-line interfaces where commands modify application state. It supports key binding display, help message formatting, and both interactive and script-driven command execution. It works with command definitions of type `'a -> 'a Lwt.t` and integrates with `Cmdtui.t` structures for command parsing and execution. Use cases include building stateful CLI tools with dynamic key bindings, interactive prompts, and scriptable command sequences.
